snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' - VS Donald J. Trump (Gulf of America) - FNF MODS [VERY HARD]
snippet.description:
randomly had this idea last week because of what's been happening

STORY:
Donald Trump signs the executive order to change the Gulf of Mexico to Gulf of America. Boyfriend is not happy about this, so he breaks into the oval office and demands that Trump change back the name. However, to change the name back, Boyfriend has to beat Trump in two songs:
- Mexico
- America

NOTE: Usually, the good ending song would be YMCA, but to avoid copyright I turned on "streamer mode", which replaced the song with what you hear in this video.

Modlink: https://gamebanana.com/mods/576508
Listen to the songs here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLH6e2Fl-x_xKT_6AVHzMu6cgMs-H38iHp

Chapters:
0:00 Menu
0:04 Mexico Dialogue
0:21 Mexico
2:35 America Dialogue
2:50 America
4:39 Good Ending
4:47 Bad Ending
5:08 End
